name: Jason Rojas Barajas
coverLetter:
I started trimming in 2014 when i came to humboldt. Been doing off and on since 2016. Me and my lady would trim 2 pounds in 4 hours seprate , i learned alot especially my method to addapt. I have a truck i can travel to and from work .I can start Now Oct.8 until Dec 2.
I been on a farm the last year in a half ,i stayed m-f up on a hill , cant do that anymore. Been doing landscape/gardening  since 2010 so i have a ton of back round work. I work good with others.
